# GCP Services (CMS)

## Cloud Run & HTTPS
- Deployed to `europe-west1`.
- Use Cloud Scheduler to trigger background jobs via HTTPS endpoints (e.g., `/api/v1/scheduler/...`).

## Cloud Storage (GCS)
- Map uploads explicitly to the correct domain bucket (e.g., `markets.thecloudarchitect.io` vs `thecloudarchitect.io`).
- Only sync the specific HTML/assets needed, avoiding full `website/` rsync where possible.

## Pub/Sub & CDN
- `PUBSUB_TOPIC_PUBLISH_ARTICLE` handles durable publish tails.
- Trigger Cloud CDN cache invalidation via URL map operations post-publish.

## Firestore
- Abide by established collection naming structures.
- Firestore emulator can be used locally.
